---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Debanjan — Senior Software Engineer"
  description="Senior software engineer, 8+ yrs. How real systems behave, break, and get debugged, plus the judgment that isn't in the code."
  ogImage="/og-image.png"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Debanjan</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Senior software engineer, 8+ yrs. How real systems behave, break, and get debugged, plus the judgment that isn't in the code.</p>

    <div class="terminal card" role="region" aria-label="Terminal hero">
      <pre><span class="prompt">$</span> whoami
backend engineer — production systems, reliability, observability

<span class="prompt">$</span> current
role: Senior Software Engineer II @ Apollo.io
focus: email deliverability, sales engagement, sequences

<span class="prompt">$</span> experience
8+ years building and operating backend systems
ruby · go · java · rails · postgres · mongodb · elasticsearch
redis · kafka · kubernetes · observability tooling

<span class="prompt">$</span> content
writing: SigNoz, Geekflare, Medium
projects: letter, bytecase (github.com/debanjanc01)

<span class="prompt">$</span> find --me
<a href="https://github.com/debanjanc01" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">github</a>   <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/debanjanc01" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">linkedin</a>   <a href="https://x.com/theybanjan" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">x</a>   <a href="mailto:debanjanc01@gmail.com">email</a>

<span class="prompt">$</span> navigate
<a href="/about">about</a>   <a href="/timeline">timeline</a>   <a href="/contact">contact</a>

# keyboard: g a → About, g c → Contact, g t → Timeline
</pre>
    </div>

    <script type="module">
      window.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
        const k = (e.key || '').toLowerCase();
        if (e.ctrlKey || e.metaKey || e.altKey) return;
        if (k === 'g') { (window as any)._g = true; return; }
        if ((window as any)._g) {
          (window as any)._g = false;
          if (k === 'a') location.href = '/about';
          else if (k === 'c') location.href = '/contact';
          else if (k === 't') location.href = '/timeline';
        }
      });
    </script>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
